            <div class="fn-entry-desc">Scaling a marketplace is not just a front-end problem. The backend — reconciliation, inventory, fulfilment — determines how long growth can hold.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="fn-entry-tag">Marketplaces</div>
        </div>

        <div class="fn-entry">
