            <div class="fn-entry-desc">Founders spend on ads before they've resolved what the brand actually stands for. The ads drive traffic to a message that doesn't convert.</div>
          </div>
          <div class="fn-entry-tag">Brand</div>
        </div>

        <div class="fn-entry">
